# Research Lab Data Management System

## Overview

This project is a console-based application for managing data in a sciences research lab. The application provides functionalities to manage experiments, samples, and researchers using Core Java, MySQL, and JDBC.

## Features

### Experiment Management
- *Add a new experiment*
- *View experiment details*
- *Update experiment information*
- *Delete an experiment*

### Sample Management
- *Add a new sample*
- *View sample details*
- *Update sample information*
- *Delete a sample*

### Researcher Management
- *Add a new researcher*
- *View researcher details*
- *Update researcher information*
- *Delete a researcher*

## Database Schema

### Experiment Table
- experiment_id (Primary Key)
- name
- description
- start_date
- end_date

### Sample Table
- sample_id (Primary Key)
- experiment_id (Foreign Key references Experiment Table)
- name
- type
- quantity

### Researcher Table
- researcher_id (Primary Key)
- name
- email
- phone_number
- specialization

## Setup

### Prerequisites
- Java Development Kit (JDK) 8 or higher
- MySQL Server
- MySQL Connector/J (JDBC Driver)
- IntelliJ IDEA or any other Java IDE
